reviewText: ASKED MY HUSBAND TO REVIEW THE MOVIE FOR ME, HE SAID, I WISH THEY HAD THIS WHEN I WAS IN BASEBALL----MY COACHES WERE NOT PREPARED IN THE 50'S---THIS WOULD HAVE REALLY HELPED ME LEARN WHAT TO DO AND HOW TO DO IT. WE CAN'T WAIT FOR THE GRT GRANDKIDS TO LEARN FROM THIS VIDEO. THANK YOU. CONNIE
